org.sql: SELECT spree_adjustments.* FROM spree_adjustments WHERE spree_adjustments.adjustable_type = "$1" AND spree_adjustments.adjustable_id IN (SELECT spree_line_items.id FROM spree_line_items WHERE spree_line_items.order_id IS NULL AND 1 = 0 ORDER BY spree_line_items.created_at ASC) AND spree_adjustments.source_type = "$2"
